The paper discusses recent approaches in robot perception, which is a subfield of robotics (cs.RO). The paper also focuses on the interaction between perception and action, which involves computer vision (cs.CV), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), and machine learning (cs.LG). Additionally, the paper discusses the use of perception in control systems, which falls under the category of systems and control (cs.SY).
